author: Michelle Deal-Zimmerman
title: WOW air offers $99 flights to Paris from Baltimore
text:
WOW air offers $99 flights to Paris from Baltimore Eiffel Tower's 125th birthday Franck Fife, AFP/Getty Images Two Bulgarian tourists pose in front of the Eiffel Tower in Paris on their last day in the capital. Two Bulgarian tourists pose in front of the Eiffel Tower in Paris on their last day in the capital. (Franck Fife, AFP/Getty Images) BWI Thurgood Marshall Airport Wow. Get from Baltimore to Paris for $99. 
WOW airline is living up to its name with an ultra low-cost fare to Paris and Amsterdam that really is, well, wow. 
The airline, which began service from BWI-Marshall Airport this year, is offering $99 one-way flights to Paris and Amsterdam this fall. 
Now, that's a deal.
